column2: SELECT TOP # A.ra, A.dec, B.distance, A.objID, B.objID as objIDMatch, A.specobjID, C.specobjIDJOIN, D.specobjIDClean FROM SpecPhotoAll AS A CROSS APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq (A.ra, A.dec, #/#.) AS B LEFT JOIN SpecPhotoAll as C on B.objID = C.objID LEFT JOIN SpecObj as D on C.specobjID = D.specobjID INTO MyDB.SpecMatch
